**/debug/*

# Ignore vscode files
**/.vscode/*

# Terraform lock files
**/plan
**/plan.out
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
.terraform.lock.hcl
*terraform*.plan
*PesterExecution*

# Others
*old*
*/old
backend.tf